<P>
   MARKET (New York) _ U.S. stocks fall sharply and the yield on
the long bond continues to decline. At 1:10 p.m., the Dow
industrial average was off 240 points, Nasdaq down 60. At midday
the long bond was up 1 12/32 point, with the yield at a record 5.42
