at the Daily News, (818) 713-3695. 
. 
MAX-FASHION (Los Angeles) Los Angeles fashion designer Max Azria
soon will be the new owner of the famous French couture house of
Herve Leger. Azria said the transaction will be complete in
September. He would not disclose the selling price. By Barbara De
Witt.
