<P>
   Eds: First pitch is at 4:05 p.m. EDT.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-DODGERS _ From consistency to chaos. That's the story for
the Dodgers since the Fox takeover. Once a model of consistency,
the Los Angeles franchise is reeling from strange change.
(Rosenberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   AJC BRAVES FARM TEAM SERIES _ Day 7
</P>
<P>
   BBO-MINORS-GREENVILLE _ GREENVILLE, S.C. _ George Lombard was
happy when Aug. 1 arrived. After weeks of hearing he might be
traded by the Braves for needed bullpen help, Lombard knows he
still has a chance to reach the majors in his hometown. After
turning down a football scholarship at Georgia to sign with
Atlanta, the private school graduate struggled for his first four
seasons. But now he is showing the talent that the Braves always
thought he would. (Curtright, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8
p.m. ET.
