Reyes. ``I'd like to see Reyes have a good September to vault him
into next year, give him a little confidence boost going into
spring training next year,'' the Cincinnati Reds manager said.
September? How about August? On a recent night, the 21-year-old
Reyes cranked up his fourth straight excellent August start for the
Reds. (McCoy, Dayton Daily News) MOVED.
