and pastor of a megachurch between Fort Worth and Dallas. In his
latest book, ``The Lady, Her Lover, and Her Lord,'' Jakes says that
men often don't use verbal communication to express their deepest
emotions. ``Men seldom speak love with words,'' he asserts. ``We
speak love in glistening eyes. We speak it in heavy sighs and
tender smiles.'' By JIM JONES. Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle
