<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Saturday, Aug. 22. The NYT frontpage advisory, with layout
description, will move by 7:30 p.m. ET. The N.Y. Times News Service
Night Supervisor is Tim Hilchey; phone: (888) 346-9867; e-mail:
hilchey(at)nytimes.com.
