<P>
   US-STRIKE (Washington) -- US intelligence, hampered by heavy
cloud cover, was unsure if missiles killed any of the terrorists at
the site targeted by the United States in Afghanistan. By Brian
McGroroy. 1200 words. (i and a coding)
</P>
