<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-21 19:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6605 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ATTACK-ALBANIA-400&AMP;AD     08-21 0707
