<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-21 20:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6697 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ATTACK-ISLAM-500&AMP;ADD-     08-21 0810
