<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-21 20:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6750 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBC-FSU-BOX-COX     08-21 0172
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FBC-FSU-BOX-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Florida State fact box
 &HT;    By Tony Barnhart
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Location: Tallahassee, FL.
</P>
<P>
   Enrollment: 30,200.
</P>
<P>
   Coach: Bobby Bowden is 208-51-4 in 23 years at Florida State,
281-83-4 overall.
</P>
<P>
   Nickname: Seminoles.
</P>
<P>
   Stadium: Doak-Campbell (80,000).
</P>
<P>
   All-time record: 358-181-17.
</P>
<P>
   ACC championships: 6 (1992, 1993, 1994, 1995-tie, 1996, 1997).
</P>
<P>
   1997 record: 11-1, 8-0 ACC.
</P>
<P>
   Schedule: Aug. 31 vs. Texas A&AMP;M, Sep. 12 at N.C. State, Sep. 19
vs. Duke, Sep. 26 vs. Southern Cal, Oct. 3 at Maryland, Oct. 10 at
Miami, Oct. 17 vs. Clemson, Oct. 24 at Georgia Tech, Oct. 31 vs.
North Carolina, Nov. 7 vs. Virginia, Nov. 14 at Wake Forest, Nov.
21 vs. Florida.
</P>
