   EARN-JOB-TENURE (Undated) _ Contrary to popular belief that
corporate downsizing and job-hopping has eroded job stability,
private studies and Government data now show that job stability has
changed remarkably little and is not on the decline at all. By
Susan J. Wells. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   SPEND
</P>
<P>
   SPEND-COLLEGE-EDUC (Undated) _ Thanks to recent tax law changes,
parents saving for a child's college education have a number of
increasingly attractive options. But are the prepaid plans a smart
way to save? By Anne Tergeson. (Moved). Graphic.
</P>
<P>
   SPEND-PRODUCTS (Undated) _ Some companies try to obscure just
what they charge for a variety of products. By Robert D. Hershey
Jr. (Moved).
</P>
