Gatsbyesque, upper-class living, which seems preserved in aspic.
Just 30 miles from Manhattan, it is a land of French manor houses,
private dirt roads and small shops selling monogrammed
wastebaskets. The respect for life's little niceties would bring a
smile to Emily Post. By Monique Yazigi. (Moved). Photo. &QL; 
