   (NYT20) PHILADELPHIA -- Aug. 21, 1998 -- ALLEGHENY-COLLAPSE,
8-21 -- A centerpiece of the expansion mapped by Sharif Abdelhak
was the creation of Allegheny University of the Health Sciences. A
month ago, with debts of $1.3 billion and recent losses of $1
million a day, Allegheny filed for protection from creditors under
Chapter 11 of the federal bankruptcy law. (Tim Shaffer/New York
Times Photo)
