AUG. 23 -- EARN-STOCK-OPTIONS, 8-21 -- The proliferation of stock
options for executives is making property settlements in divorces
more contentious. Kim Hislop and her husband, John, divorced in
1994; she is seeking a 50-50 split of the value his options. (Judy
Griesedieck/New York Times Photo)
